<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1944-02-18T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1944-02-18T00:00:00-05:00" n="92" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d92">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">740.00119 EAC/126</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">Memorandum by President <persName type="from">Roosevelt</persName> to the <gloss type="to">Acting Secretary
                                    of State</gloss>
                            </hi>
                        </head>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1944-02-18">February 18,
                                1944</date>.</dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>What are the zones in the British and Russian drafts and what is the zone
                            we are proposing? I must know this in order that it conform with what I
                            decided on months ago.</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>F[<hi rend="smallcaps">ranklin</hi>] D. R[<hi rend="smallcaps">oosevelt</hi>]</signed>
                        </closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>